About WeebIRC:
WeebIRC is basically a very, very simple irc client focussed on retreiving anime through XDCC. It implements www.nibl.co.uk in a way that you can search and directly download your anime without having to copy paste everything. It originally started as a simple appliction which only goal was to able the user to batch download a whole anime through XDCC, but, I suppose that adding a single download wasn't to dificult to realize. Therefor I added more and more till it became a fully functionally download hub for anime.
This application is still in alpha stadium, many things might go wrong and therefore I am not responsible for whatever happens while you use this application.
Things that might happen:
-Due to an error it cannot start the download and will spam the bot which can cause a (temporary) ban -Due to your location you might get caught for downloading illigally. -Due to your computer being a cardbox it might catch fire and burn your whole place down -Due to you not paying attention you might suddenly download a virus... shit happens. -Due to you being at the wrong place, at the wrong time, you die...
Anyway, this is all just a fun application I made in my free time to let me become more lazy. I hope that this can be of use for someone :D.
